   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:27:44,716:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 8. Causal Enclosure Loss + Discrete Markov Transition Model
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:27:44,727:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  -- Adversarial probe with gradient reversal that
