   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:27:45,095:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The baseline probe as a coarse-grained Markov model.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:27:45,101:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  The baseline probe maps 
