   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:27:45,227:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  -- this is exactly a discrete, action-conditioned Markov
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:27:45,235:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: transition kernel over the (chart, code) state space. At inference time, this probe can be used as a 
