   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:27:56,871:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 5.3 Why This Works: Inverse Optimal Control via Hamiltonian Fitting
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:27:56,879:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The theoretical justification connects to classical optimal control. The Hamiltonian integrator solves:
