   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,016:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |---|---|---|
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,021:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,033:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Any base model
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,077:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Frozen backbone + geometric shell |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,089:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Same encoder wraps SmolVLA, ViT, or any feature extractor |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,096:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,102:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
