   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,240:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Symplectic integrator | Energy conservation bounded |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,246:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,252:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,260:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Sample efficiency
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,274:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Regime/nuisance/texture split removes redundancy | Fewer epochs to convergence |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,280:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,286:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,294:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Hard
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,301:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: safety
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,314:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Sieve contracts halt on violation | Zero silent failures |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,321:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,327:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,336:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Causal latent decomposition
