   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,585:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Routing stability
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,610:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Zeno loss (JSD on consecutive routing) | Chart flip rate bounded,
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 12:28:01,618:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: no chattering |
